{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-layouts"
    }
%}
    {% block component_scrollspy_section_content %}
        <h3>Layouts</h3>
        <h4>Site Layout</h4>
        <p>The Site Layout component provides a generally framework for a NDS page using Twig block statements. The main regions defined in the pattern are header, global_navigation, hero, main, and footer. The block statements that define these regions are only visible in the Twig file. The HTML structure of Site Layout is very plain, allowing you to define your own markup with almost full flexibility:</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" with
            {
                "component_snippet_show_rendered": "no"
            }
        %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/layouts/layouts-site/_layouts-site-main.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Main Layout</h4>
        <p>The Main Layout component defines the major sections of an NDS page. The component provides three main columns: left, main, and right.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" with
            {
                "component_snippet_show_rendered": "no"
            }
        %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/layouts/layouts-main/_layouts-main-main.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Body Card</h4>
        <p>The Body Card component is used to display a page's main content. This component handles padding at various breakpoints, ensuring a visually appealing experience regardless of device or browser.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" with
            {
                "component_snippet_show_rendered": "no"
            }
        %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/layouts/layouts-body/_layouts-body-main.twig" with
                    {
                        "layouts_body_vertical_padding": "yes"
                    }
                %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
<hr>
{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-links"
    }
%}
    {% block component_scrollspy_section_content %}
        <h3>Links</h3>
        <p>Links are used to take website users from page to page. NDS uses a bottom-border instead of an underline to make links look more elegant.</p>
        <h4>Default Link</h4>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/links/link-default/demo/link-default.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>External Link</h4>
        <p>NDS requires that all external links - links that direct users away from the current site they are viewing - are designated with the Font Awesome external link icon. Out of the box, NDS uses JS to automatically append these icons. A notable exception to this policy is links to social media (i.e. Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, etc.) when they are presented in the form of a button.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/links/link-external/demo/link-external.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Link with Icon</h4>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/links/link-icon/demo/link-icon-left.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
<hr>
{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-media"
    }
%}
    {% block component_scrollspy_section_content %}
        <h3>Media</h3>
        <p>Audio and video can be effective ways to communicate with your audience, however, each comes with a variety of accessibility requirements. Please review the <a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/media/av/">guidelines from W3C on how to make your audio and video accessible.</a></p>
        <h4>Audio</h4>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/media/media-audio/demo/media-audio.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Video</h4>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/media/media-video/demo/media-video.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>YouTube Video</h4>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/media/media-video-youtube/demo/media-video-youtube.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
<hr>
{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-tables"
    }
%}
    {% block component_scrollspy_section_content %}
        <h3>Tables</h3>
        <p>Tables can be tricky on the web for accessibility and responsive reasons. NDS employs <a href="https://datatables.net/">DataTables</a> to create properly formatted, simple tables to and improve the experience of tables across devices. Adding the custom attribute nds-datatable="true" to the table tag will initialize the responsive functionality of Datatables.</p>
        {% include "@atoms/text/text-uswds/_text-uswds-main.twig" with
            {
                "text_uswds_component_name": "Tables",
                "text_uswds_href": "https://designsystem.digital.gov/components/table/"
            }
        %}
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/tables/table-default/demo/table-default.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
<hr>
{% embed "@molecules/components/component-scrollspy-section/_component-scrollspy-section-main.twig" with
    {
        "component_scrollspy_section_id": "section-components-atoms-text"
    }
%}
    {% block component_scrollspy_section_content %}
        <h3>Text</h3>
        <h4>Blockquote</h4>
        <p>Blockquotes are useful to separate quotes from the rest of the body text, adding visual interest to pages and highlighting the quote.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/text/text-blockquote/demo/text-blockquote.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Badge</h4>
        <p>Badges are static, non-functional indicators of information. Typically badges are used to showcase tags and metadata of certain components, like search results.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/text/text-badge/demo/text-badge.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Chip</h4>
        <p>Chips are functional indicators of search and filter results. NDS uses a search style wherein selected filters are displayed using chips, allowing users to see exactly what they have searched and filtered on. Selecting the 'x' in the chip should remove the filter from the search.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/text/text-chip/demo/text-chip.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Heading with Icon</h4>
        <p>This component allows users to include a Font Awesome icon next to a heading.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/text/text-heading-icon/demo/text-heading-icon.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Image Credit &amp; Caption</h4>
        <p>NDS strongly suggests captioning and crediting your images to bolster accessibility and to properly cite sources. The easiest way to use this pattern is by leveraging the Media Component (molecule: component-media), negating the need to use this pattern on its own.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/text/text-image-credit-caption/demo/text-image-credit-caption.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}

        <h4>Search Results</h4>
        <p>When displaying a set of search results, it is a best practice to include the number of overall results returned. The Search Results component provides a display for this purpose. Place this component directly above the listing of search results.</p>
        {% embed "@molecules/components/component-snippet/_component-snippet-main.twig" %}
            {% block component_snippet_code %}
                {% include "@nds/01-atoms/text/text-search-results/demo/text-search-results.twig" %}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endembed %}
    {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
<hr>